The primary audience for this prototype is the child who  will be using the device.  
Children have small attention plans, low knowledge.

The secondary audidence will be the parents of the child using the device.
Specific wants and needs for what their child will accomplish. They will have better knowledge of the software.

The device to be used is a mobile device and has Android OS. The app needs to be a simple UI and the display would be that of books on a bookshelf. The interaction type will be that of clicking and swiping. 
The parents would start the account for the child, and the child has usage of all books but does not have access to the account info.
To access the account info the parents will have to use a password.
